title: #419 CROWDER'S THANKSGIVING EXTRAVAGANZA! | Nicole Arbour Guests | Louder With Crowder
description: It's our last show until the new year, so we're going out with a bang! Talking all things Michael Creepy Porn Woman Beating Lawyer (allegedly) Avenatti, Jim Acosta's continued saga, and rebutting the Young Turks who think the Bible is pro-abortion. Hint: not even close. Nicole Arbour joins us to discuss the fires in California, then plays Hipster or Hobo. The always hilarious Owen Benjamin sits third chair.
